title: US Hottest Summers and Coldest Winters, USA,
name: US Hottest Summers and Coldest Winters, USA,
description: This dataset illustrates the cities with more than 50,000 people that have had the hottest summers and the coldest winters.  Other attributtes include the original ranking, the inverse ranking (use only for mapping purposes only), the population, the city and state, and the degrees in Fahrenheit.  A value of -1 means that the data was not applicable.Source: City-DataURL:  http://www.city-data.com/top2/c455.htmlhttp://www.city-data.com/top2/c456.htmlDate Accessed:  November 7, 2007
